68   def getEventData(group: String, id: String): Future[Option[Model.Event]] = {
69     val request = ws.url(config.url + group + "/events/" + id)
70       .addQueryStringParameters("key" -> config.apiKey, "fields" -> "time,photo_album,group_category")
71       
72     val result = request.get()
73 
74     result.map { case x =>
75       log.debug("Got response from meetup api: " + x.body)
76       val res = x.json.validate[Model.Event]
77       log.debug(res.toString())
78       res.asOpt
79     }
80   }
81 
82   def getEvent(url: String, login: Login): Future[Option[EventDetail]] = {
83     val t = new URI(url).getPath.split("/")
84     val i = t.indexOf("events")
85     getEventData(t(i-1),t(i+1)).flatMap {
86       case Some(e) => toEventDetail(e).map(Some(_))
87       case None => Future.successful(None)
88     }
89   }
90 
91   def canImport(url: String, login: Login) = {
92     val uri = new URI(url)
93     val split = uri.getPath.split("/").indexOf("events")
94     (uri.getHost.equals("www.meetup.com") || uri.getHost.equals("www.meetup.de")) && split >= 0
95   }
96 
97   def toEventDetail(data: Model.Event): Future[EventDetail] = {
98     val loc = data.venue match {
99       case Some(x) => {
100         if(x.zip.isDefined)
101           Future.successful(Location(None, x.name, Some(x.lat), Some(x.lon),
102                             x.country, x.city, x.street.getOrElse(x.address_1.getOrElse("")), None,
103                             x.phone, None, None, x.zip))
104         else {
105           geocoder.getZip(Geocoder.Address(x.country, x.city, x.street.getOrElse(x.address_1.getOrElse("")))).map {
106             case zip => Location(None, x.name, Some(x.lat), Some(x.lon),
107                             x.country, x.city, x.street.getOrElse(x.address_1.getOrElse("")), None,
108                             x.phone, None, None, zip)
109           }
110         }
111       }
112       case None => Future.successful(Location(None,"",None,None,"","","",None,None,None,None,None))
113     }
114 
115     val from = new Timestamp(data.time)
116 
117     lazy val descText = XhtmlParser(new BufferedSource(new ByteArrayInputStream(("<p>" ++ data.description ++ "</p>").getBytes))).text
118     
119     val description = data.plain_text_no_images_description
120       .orElse(data.plain_text_description)
121       .getOrElse(descText)
122     
123     val categories = categoryMap.getOrElse(data.group.category.shortname,List()) ++ List(c.meetup)
124     
125     loc.map {
126       case l => EventDetail(None, data.name, from,
127                 None, description,
128                 Organizer(None,"Organizer",-1,None), categories,
129                 None, l,
130                 data.photo_album.map(_.photo_sample).getOrElse(List()).map(x => TaggedImage(None,None,None,Some(x.photo_link))), 0,
131                 None, None) //TODO Prices
132     }
133   }
134 }
